Jawan is a high-octane action thriller which outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in society.

Dance with me now I can‚Äôt break away
Aaj sari fikreiin tu shake away
Shake away
Dil thirakta dance wale groove pe
Nachun mai to step mera vekh ve

Vekh ve
Aaj sare kaam kal pe talke
Tak dhina dhin nache jayein taal pe
Disko jaz blues sare bhoolke
Desi wale geet pe tu jhoolke
Pehle kiya chaiya chaiya re
Ab kar tha tha thaiyya
Ramiya vasta vaiya..!

Sama mazedar hua houle houle

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.title: Two types of husband | Awareness | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
Antenatal care (ANC) plays a pivotal role in ensuring a healthy pregnancy and safe childbirth. Regular ANC check-ups help monitor the health of both the mother and the developing fetus, enabling early detection and management of potential complications. When it comes to childbirth, opting for institutional delivery in a healthcare facility under skilled birth attendants significantly reduces maternal and neonatal mortality rates. These controlled environments provide necessary medical interventions and emergency care if required during labor and delivery. Moreover, after birth, timely and comprehensive child vaccinations are crucial to protect infants from various preventable diseases, building their immune system and ensuring a healthy start to life. Vaccinations safeguard children's health and contribute to the overall well-being of the community by preventing the spread of contagious illnesses.
This video is produced by
Peren District Administration under Beti Bacho Beti Padhao (BBBP) on Girl child/Women health related issues.

localized.title: Two types of husband | Awareness | Dreamz Unlimited
localized.description:
Antenatal care (ANC) plays a pivotal role in ensuring a healthy pregnancy and safe childbirth. Regular ANC check-ups help monitor the health of both the mother and the developing fetus, enabling early detection and management of potential complications. When it comes to childbirth, opting for institutional delivery in a healthcare facility under skilled birth attendants significantly reduces maternal and neonatal mortality rates. These controlled environments provide necessary medical interventions and emergency care if required during labor and delivery. Moreover, after birth, timely and comprehensive child vaccinations are crucial to protect infants from various preventable diseases, building their immune system and ensuring a healthy start to life. Vaccinations safeguard children's health and contribute to the overall well-being of the community by preventing the spread of contagious illnesses.
This video is produced by
Peren District Administration under Beti Bacho Beti Padhao (BBBP) on Girl child/Women health related issues.

snippet.title: Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom | Trailer
snippet.description:
One king will lead us all. #Aquaman and the Lost Kingdom - Only in theaters December 20.

Director James Wan and Aquaman himself, Jason Momoa‚Äîalong with Patrick Wilson, Amber Heard, Yahya Abdul-Mateen II and Nicole Kidman‚Äîreturn in the sequel to the highest-grossing DC film of all time: ‚ÄúAquaman and the Lost Kingdom.‚Äù

Having failed to defeat Aquaman the first time, Black Manta, still driven by the need to avenge his father‚Äôs death, will stop at nothing to take Aquaman down once and for all. This time Black Manta is more formidable than ever before, wielding the power of the mythic Black Trident, which unleashes an ancient and malevolent force. To defeat him, Aquaman will turn to his imprisoned brother Orm, the former King of Atlantis, to forge an unlikely alliance. Together, they must set aside their differences in order to protect their kingdom and save Aquaman‚Äôs family, and the world, from irreversible destruction.

All returning to the roles they originated, Jason Momoa plays Arthur Curry/Aquaman, now balancing his duties as both the King of Atlantis and a new father; Patrick Wilson is Orm, Aquaman‚Äôs half-brother and his nemesis, who must now step into a new role as his brother‚Äôs reluctant ally; Amber Heard is Mera, Atlantis‚Äô Queen and mother of the heir to the throne; Yahya Abdul-Mateen II is Black Manta, committed more than ever to avenge his father‚Äôs death by destroying Aquaman, his family and Atlantis; and Nicole Kidman as Atlanna, a fierce leader and mother with the heart of a warrior. Also reprising their roles are Dolph Lundgren as King Nereus and Randall Park as Dr. Stephen Shin.

Directed by Wan, ‚ÄúAquaman and the Lost Kingdom‚Äù is produced by Peter Safran, Wan and Rob Cowan. The executive producers are Galen Vaisman and Walter Hamada.

The screenplay is by David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, from a story by James Wan & David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick and Jason Momoa & Thomas Pa‚Äôa Sibbett, based on characters from DC, Aquaman created by Paul Norris and Mort Weisinger. 

Joining Wan behind-the-camera is his sterling team of ‚ÄúAquaman‚Äù artisans: director of photography Don Burgess (‚ÄúThe Conjuring 2‚Äù), production designer Bill Brzeski (‚ÄúJumanji: The Next Level‚Äù), editor Kirk Morri (‚ÄúFurious 7‚Äù), composer Rupert Gregson-Williams (‚ÄúWonder Woman‚Äù) and music supervisor is Michelle Silverman (‚ÄúMalignant‚Äù). Visual effects supervisor Nick Davis (‚ÄúThe Clash of the Titans‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Dark Knight‚Äù) and costume designer Richard Sale (‚ÄúDoctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness,‚Äù ‚ÄúReady Player One‚Äù) also join.

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents An Atomic Monster / A Peter Safran Production of A James Wan Film, ‚ÄúAquaman and the Lost Kingdom,‚Äù set to open in theaters internationally beginning 20 December 2023 and in North America on December 20, 2023; it will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: #kirtimehra ‡§ñ‡•Å‡§¶ ‡§ï‡§æ ‡§®‡§æ‡§Æ ‡§¨‡§®‡§æ‡§®‡•á ‡§ï‡•Ä ‡§ï‡§π‡§æ‡§®‡•Ä | @KirtiMehra | Kirti Mehra | Josh Talks Hindi |
snippet.description:
#kirtimehra is a well-known #youtuber . She has talked openly about all aspects of her #life. How she created a #youtubechannel and what was her journey to get here She also became emotional, remembering many incidents in her life. There came a time in her life when she lived on salt and bread. Kirti Mehra's father had a dream that his daughter would someday be on TV. snippet.title: DESH KA DHONI | OFFICIAL TRAILER | Flying Beast
snippet.description:
It's the story of a middle-class, hard-working man, whose journey began in Kanpur.  Like any other middle-class guy, he chooses to attend IIT under parental pressure rather than chasing his passion to become a cricketer. Lingering within him is the remorse of never affording his passion the opportunity it deserved.

He idolized Mr. MS Dhoni, who didn't give up and was persistent in achieving his dreams and passion of becoming a cricketer, irrespective of every possible hurdle in life.
His decision to portray his love for his idol through his hard work, which is unparalleled.

Gaurav then, gets on a maiden mammoth journey of a 2400km bicycle ride from Delhi to Chennai in the extreme weather and heat conditions of the month of May to pay a legendary tribute to MS Dhoni by collecting wishes for him, all across the country.

snippet.title: Introducing iPhone 15 Pro | Apple
snippet.description:
The new iPhone 15 Pro and iPhone 15 Pro Max are ready for action. Built with aerospace-grade titanium for our lightest, most powerful Pro models ever.

The new Pro camera system pushes the limits of what‚Äôs possible on a smartphone, giving photographers the equivalent of seven pro lenses ranging from 13 mm on the Ultra Wide camera to 120 mm on the 5x Telephoto camera on iPhone 15 Pro Max.

Filmmakers can now record video in ProRes 4K at 60 fps directly to an external drive. The addition of a USB-C connector brings superfast USB 3 transfer speeds, along with support for pro formats that massively improve the workflow between shooting and post-production.

The new design also includes a customizable Action button for quicker access to your favorite feature.*

And the A17 Pro chip with a 6-core GPU introduces a whole new level of immersive mobile gaming performance. 

In short, the new titanium iPhone 15 Pro is our most powerful photo-taking, movie-making, game-playing iPhone ever.

Learn more about iPhone 15 Pro and iPhone 15 Pro Max: https://apple.co/3PBuiJq

Audio Descriptions: https://apple.co/44QCI3W

Episode 3877: B.K. Su
--------------------------------------------------------
Purush Mandali of Gokuldham converses about business at Taarak's house. Jetha reaches home and is shocked to find the door open. He enters the house and finds Bapuji sleeping on the couch, he tries to pick him up in his hands and shift him into his bedroom but he wakes up and gets frightened.  Jetha asks Bhide to publish his book of thoughts but later disagrees with Bhide's 'suvichaar' on the society board as he finds it wrong What happens next? Watch the episode to learn more!!

snippet.description:
Discover your full potential in Data Science with SCALER's skill-enhancing programs. On August 23rd, India made history by achieving a South Pole lunar landing with Chandrayaan-3. Following the 2008 Jawahar Point mission, India gained a new landing site called Shiv Shakti Point. In the two-week mission, the Vikram Lander and Pragyan Rover made groundbreaking discoveries on the moon. After these accomplishments, they entered sleep mode on September 4th, with plans to awaken in a week. Initially, there was a two-week research window, but possibilities for extension have arisen. How is this possible, and what new discoveries have come from Chandrayaan-3's experiments? Let's explore together in this video by Dhruv Rathee.

en.description:

Check out:  https://www.scaler.com/?utm_source=brandedcontent&utm_medium=DhruvRatheeSeptember2023&utm_campaign=brand_scaler_academy_brandedcontent_DhruvRatheeSeptember2023_branded-content-video-campaign-DhruvRatheeSeptember2023-15September2023_india_all&utm_id=brandedcontent&utm_content=YT-description

On August 23rd, India made history by achieving a South Pole lunar landing with Chandrayaan-3. Following the 2008 Jawahar Point mission, India gained a new landing site called Shiv Shakti Point. In the two-week mission, the Vikram Lander and Pragyan Rover made groundbreaking discoveries on the moon. After these accomplishments, they entered sleep mode on September 4th, with plans to awaken in a week. Initially, there was a two-week research window, but possibilities for extension have arisen. How is this possible, and what new discoveries have come from Chandrayaan-3's experiments? Let's explore together in this video by Dhruv Rathee.

snippet.title: INDIA alliance boycotts 14 anchors, MBS & Modi‚Äôs friendship becomes primetime news | TV Newsance 226
snippet.description:
#g20summit #indiaalliance #TVNewsance

The TV news anchors had a field day with the G20 Summit, and it did not end there. As the Saudi crown prince, Mohammad Bin Salman alias MBS, stayed back after the G20 meet for his official state visit, the television media blew up with visuals of ‚ÄúModi and MBS‚Äô friendship‚Äù. 

Rubika counted the similarities between the two leaders, while Syed Suhail narrated the story of Modi playing peacemaker between MBS and US president Joe Biden. Zee News divulged what all happened after MBS ‚Äúran to hug Modi‚Äù. Meanwhile, Sushant got a chance to meet PM Modi along with MBS at the Rashtrapati Bhavan. And it compelled us to take a trip down memory lane to look at his views on Arab countries. 

The big news this week was that the 12-member opposition INDIA alliance has decided to boycott 14 news anchors across nine channels for their communal and hate-filled debates. This resulted in the anchors hitting back, accompanied by a lot of hysteria and drama.

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.
